      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It\u2019s in truly pristine shape and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
