    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 wide-body silhouette. Powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the powerplant delivers linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The viscous-clutch AWD system ensures exceptional mechanical grip, while the Turbo-derived suspension and four-piston monoblock calipers provide surgical handling and fade-free deceleration. This specimen boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, ensuring long-term reliability. The Arctic Silver Metallic finish remains flawless, covering a chassis with zero structural compromises. An enthusiast-grade offering for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
