      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no signs of wear, and every surface remains tactile and factory-fresh. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive service log included. Always garage-kept under a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
